buyerAgent.name: Tracey L. Nygren CRS, GRI, CNE

data.description: This home has everything you've been searching for! Five bedrooms (6 with a nonconforming in the finished basement), 2.5 bathrooms, formal dining area, 3 season screened in porch, 2 fireplaces, and a fully fenced in yard. The eat in kitchen has beautiful cherry wood cabinetry with windows overlooking the back yard. Upstairs you'll find the primary bedroom with dual closets and an en suite. Four additional bedrooms and full bathroom on the second level. Fall in love with the established neighborhood charm - close proximity to schools and parks. With over 2600 total sqft finish, this home has the space to fit a variety of needs. With some added personal touches, make this house a home! Call your favorite realtor for a showing today.
